Reasoning: The paper discusses a hierarchical architecture based on neural networks for classification with large hierarchical labels. This falls under the domain of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered by the cs.LG and cs.AI sub-categories. The use of neural networks also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the cs.NE (neural and evolutionary computing) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of the architecture for image classification, which falls under the domains of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
